cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with the segmentation of histopathology sections using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of machine learning techniques, specifically deep learning, is also a prominent aspect of the paper, which suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves image processing and analysis, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
